                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p>Connect2us is South Africa's premier online platform for literature, connecting book lovers with a vast collection of books across all genres. We offer a curated selection of local and international titles, competitive prices, and fast delivery throughout South Africa.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item mb-3 border rounded shadow-sm">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading2">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
                                    Where are you located?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2" data-bs-parent="#generalAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p>Our headquarters are located in Cape Town, South Africa, but we ship books nationwide. We have distribution centers in major cities including Johannesburg, Durban, and Cape Town to ensure fast delivery.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item mb-3 border rounded shadow-sm">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading3">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
                                    Do you have a physical store?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading3" data-bs-parent="#generalAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p>Currently, Connect2us operates exclusively online. This allows us to offer competitive prices and a wider selection of books. However, we're exploring options for physical locations in the future.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item mb-3 border rounded shadow-sm">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading4">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
                                    What types of books do you sell?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading4" data-bs-parent="#generalAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p>We offer a wide variety of books including fiction, non-fiction, academic textbooks, children's books, self-help, business, technology, and South African literature. We also stock rare and collectible books.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
